    <div class="list">
      <h4 id="outline"> Outline Course</h4>
      <ol>
        <li class="li-outline">Introduction to data analysis tools in Python</li>
        <li class="li-outline"> Descriptive statistics</li>
        <li class="li-outline">Data structures with Pandas</li>
        <li class="li-outline">ntroductory hypothesis testing and statistical inference</li>
        <li class="li-outline">Data visualization</li>
        <li class="li-outline">Cleaning and reformatting messy datasets using regular expressions or dedicated tools such as open refine</li>
        <li class="li-outline">Natural language processing</li>
